---
title: Middle Eastern Yoghurt Chicken & Roast Veggie Couscous for Dinner with a Chicken & Kumara Salad with Yoghurt Dressing for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new twist on the recipe to create
something different for lunch the next day! Combine our popular chermoula spice mix with yoghurt for a tasty
marinade that keeps chicken strips tasty and tender over a bed of fragrant couscous and veggies. At lunch, transform
it into a colourful roast kumara salad with crumbly cheese for a guaranteed flavour sensation.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

